                        "created_at": "1768038231",
                        "id": "17914893855254175",
                        "text": "Part 2 of Must-Buy Items in Japan \ud83c\uddef\ud83c\uddf5\ud83d\udc95\n\u2028Save this for your next Japan trip!\n\nI did a lot of research on skincare and fashion items to buy in Japan, so feel free to steal this list \ud83d\ude03\n\nPro Tips:\n* Buy Onitsuka Tiger shoes from Tokyo as there are multiple outlet options compared to Kyoto or Osaka\n* Don\u2019t forget to buy Omamori which are Japanese good luck charms for prosperity, good health, success in studies and more. These are usually sold near temples\n* Souvenir shopping is best around Sensoji Temple, Asakusa. Here you\u2019ll find plenty of options at more affordable prices\n* Always carry your passport for tax-free shopping\n* Shop from Uniqlo for high quality clothing at reasonable prices. They also have great bag options\n\nComment if you need more specific details!\nAnd don\u2019t forget to check Part 1 of Must buys in Japan \ud83d\udc95\n\n#japan #traveljapan #japanshopping #travel #tokyo"
                    }
                }
            ]
